:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >有效期内的营业执照</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅行社责任险</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >4、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >机构代码证</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >5、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >税务登记证</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:36.0000pt; text-indent:-36.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; " >二、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >产品内容规范</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp18  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >双方合作产品的内容，必须符合《旅行社条例》的相关规定。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp16  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >、合作产品。双方合作的专属产品（双方特别约定的，由大通独家销售的产品），不得有第三方销售及向第三方泄漏，任何一方不得对外泄漏本合同内容或有第三方销售。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp18  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、特价产品。地接社推出特价产品，能够在第一时间内告知大通计调业务中心专线分控人员。地接社销售特价线路（价格）必须传真方式与我社。地接社特价线路必须保证质量。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp18  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3.地接社所推出的旅游产品有特色，多样化。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp18  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >二、价格规范</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp16  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1、地接社提供的销售价格必须符合市场价格，不得高于市场价。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp16  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、地接社销售价格因市场原因需调整，要及时通知大通计调业务中心专线分控人员</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp16  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >三、操作规范</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp16  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1、完全依照双方签订的协议、接待质量安全协议操作，保证旅游质量。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、地接社</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >必须严格按照双方已确认的行程及标准操作（有购物点的，明确安排的购物次数、停留时间及购物场所的名称。明确旅游者自由活动的时间和次数。明确游览项目的具体内容和时间）。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >四、服务质量优先</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >地接社必须在线路确定的同时向大通提出该线路的各个环节注意事项，特别是可能引起人身财产安全的事项，以便大通在销售过程中及时告知游客；同时，地接社应保证地接团队旅游行程中游客、导游及领队的人身财产安全。&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（1）&nbsp;人身安全</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;地接社在接待大通游客时，必须保证在当地人身安全，地接社在接待过程中必须提醒游客人身安全与注意事项。地接社在接待大通游客过程中出现人身安全问题、是地接社过失或过错，大通游客所产生费用全部由地接社承担。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（2）财产安全</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;地接社在接待过程中必须保证大通游客财产安全，必须提醒游客保管好自身财产。大通游客在游览过程中发生财产被盗，地接社必须配合游客处理好相关事宜，如：稳定游客情绪，及时报警立案等。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游途中，地接社必须严格按照双方确定的住宿等级，安排好双方团队在当地的住宿，不得随意降低住宿等级。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3、</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >地接社提供的车辆需具有本省（市）公安及行业管理部门核发的正式牌照及旅游营运证件、客运资质。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >(1)旅游途中，地接社必须严格按照双方确认的用车标准，安排好大通团队在目的地的旅游。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; text-indent:-21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >(2)不得随意降低用车标准或使用非旅游定点车辆单位的车辆，对旅游定点车辆单位要加强日常行车安全（包含旅游车辆的正常保险及车上乘客保险，严禁团队车辆带故障运行）及司机规范服务（包含司机出团期间，必须身心健康，每天出车前的车辆故障检查）管理的指导和督促。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:12.0000pt; text-indent:-10.5000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >4、如因地接社服务过程中发生的质量问题、安全事故、未达到本身承诺的标准或未能保障大通游客人身、财产安全而造成的意外事故（</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; text-decoration:underline ;font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >意外事故是指包括由地接社对承担全责、主要责任、次要责任、无责的事故在内的事故</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >）造成大通游客人身或财产损害的，一切损失概均由地接社先负责，具体约定如下：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >前期救治义务：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（1）意外事故发生以后，地接社有义务配合大通一同安抚大通的受伤游客；</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; vertical-align:; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（2）由地接社全额垫付大通受伤游客前期救治所需的医疗费用；</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.00